These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, pop, gospel
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, chef, pilot
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, october, august
City: new-york, london, edinburgh
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, lizard
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
3. the chef is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
6. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of funk##1
7. the social-worker is between the owner of the chinchilla and the chef##2
8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre      | gospel     | pop      | funk      |
| Job          | chef   | social-worker   | pilot       |
| Birthday   | august | november | october    |
| City   | edinburgh  | new-york    | london    |
| Pet           | fish    | lizard    | chinchilla |
| Transport     | subway  | train     | bus        |

