.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
City: san-francisco, liverpool, venice
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, grapes, lemon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, drama
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, azalea
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, scooter
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, pink, coral
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person eating lemon is between the person who growsazalea and the person traveling to venice##2
7. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| City      | liverpool     | san-francisco        | venice      |
| Food          | grapes    | lemon       | cabbage  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | documentary | crime    |
| Flower   | azalea | rose   | poppy    |
| Transport           | motorbike      | airplane  | scooter      |
| Color         | coral    | pink      | lilac |

