2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person eating radish and the vegafina-smoker##2
9. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Game      | poker      | whist     | billiard      |
| Food          | radish     | apple     | cucumber     |
| Birthday         | september      | january | november    |
